high_descs: Turn around and head towards the sink.
Pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn around and head towards the fridge on your right.
Place the egg in the fridge, let it cool and take it back out.
Take a step to the right to find the microwave.
Place the egg inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled egg inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Take the egg out of the sink.
Open the refrigerator and place the egg inside.
Take the egg out of the refrigerator and walk to the microwave
Place the egg inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled egg inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the sink, to the right of the dishwasher.
Pick up the egg in the sink, to the left of the tomato.
Turn around, go forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Chill the egg in the fridge.
Go to the microwave, to the right of the fridge.
Put the egg in the microwave, to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold egg in the microwave.
